OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1781603304
OL,3,CMother of baby murdered by teacher was
OL,4,Cjailed for murdering pensioner
OL,6,FThe mother of a baby who was sexually
OL,7,Fassaulted and murdered by a man trying
OL,8,Fto adopt him served jail time in 1999
OL,9,Ffor murdering a 71-year-old widow, it
OL,10,Fhas emerged.
OL,12,FPreston Davey was taken from his
OL,13,Fmother Sarah Davey under an emergency
OL,14,Fcare order obtained by Oldham Council.
OL,16,FHe was put into foster care where he
OL,17,Fstayed and thrived until being adopted
OL,18,Fby Jamie Varley and John McGowan-
OL,19,FFazakerley.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
