PN,36502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1781603304
OL,3,CMother of baby murdered by teacher was
OL,4,Cjailed for murdering pensioner
OL,6,FIn the four months he was in their
OL,7,Fcare, he was routinely ill-treated,
OL,8,Fsexually abused and physically
OL,9,Fassaulted, suffering 40 traumatic
OL,10,Finjuries. He also had indecent images
OL,11,Fand videos taken of him.
OL,13,FPreston died at the hands of Varley in
OL,14,FJuly 2023.
OL,16,FHis mother had been in and out of jail
OL,17,Fafter being given a mandatory life
OL,18,Fsentence for murder in July 1999.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
