PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1781603304
OL,3,CMother of baby murdered by teacher was
OL,4,Cjailed for murdering pensioner
OL,6,FDavey had some contact with her son
OL,7,Fand did register his birth, giving her
OL,8,Foccupation as hairdresser and her
OL,9,Faddress as the mother and baby until
OL,10,Fat HMP Styal.
OL,12,FSarah was aged just 14 when she was
OL,13,Fordered to serve a minimum of eight
OL,14,Fyears and one day for the horrific
OL,15,Fmurder of widow, Lily Lilley, in
OL,16,FFailsworth, Oldham in September 1998.
OL,18,FDavey, along with a 15-year-old
OL,19,Ffriend, Lisa Healey, befriended the
OL,20,Ffrail pensioner, a grandmother of
OL,21,Fthree, at local shops.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
