PN,36504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1781603304
OL,3,CMother of baby murdered by teacher was
OL,4,Cjailed for murdering pensioner
OL,6,FShe invited them into her home for a
OL,7,Fcup of tea and the pair then brutally
OL,8,Ftortured Lily by squirting shampoo in
OL,9,Fher eyes, cutting her with a knife and
OL,10,Ftying a gag round her mouth so tightly
OL,11,Fthat her dentures were forced down her
OL,12,Fthroat, choking her to death.
OL,14,FThey then crammed her lifeless body
OL,15,Finto a bin and, laughing and giggling,
OL,16,Fwalked it through the streets before
OL,17,Fthrowing it in the Rochdale Canal.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
