PN,36505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1781603304
OL,3,CMother of baby murdered by teacher was
OL,4,Cjailed for murdering pensioner
OL,6,FAfter the killing they made hundreds
OL,7,Fof calls from her phone, used her
OL,8,Fpension money to buy crisps and
OL,9,Fchocolate and trashed her home.
OL,11,FThe trial judge, Mr Justice Sachs,
OL,12,Fdescribed the crime as "unspeakably
OL,13,Fwicked".
OL,15,FDavey has been released and recalled
OL,16,Fto prison on three occasions,
OL,17,Faccording to the Parole Board.
OL,26,@tD@XOUuD@GO]
