OL,3,CMother of baby murdered by teacher was
OL,4,Cjailed for murdering pensioner
OL,6,FOn the last occasion she was released
OL,7,Fin August 2021 but recalled to custody
OL,8,Fon 2 November 2021 for an unspecified
OL,9,Fbreach of her terms of release. It is
OL,10,Fduring this period she became pregnant
OL,11,Fwith Preston.
OL,13,FMs Davey, now aged 42, has attended
OL,14,Fparts of the trial of Varley and
OL,15,FMcGowan-Fazakerley.
OL,17,FThe terms of her current release from
OL,18,Fcustody, her licence conditions,
OL,19,Finclude good behaviour, to disclose
OL,20,Frelationships and enhanced drug
OL,21,Fmonitoring.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
